# For larger n, we can't check optimality, but ensure the program runs quickly
import time
arr = [random.randint(0,10**9) for _ in range(200000)]
start = time.time()
p = Popen(["/opt/openhands-venv/bin/python3","solution.py"], stdin=PIPE, stdout=PIPE, stderr=PIPE, text=True)
out,err = p.communicate(str(len(arr))+'\n'+' '.join(map(str,arr))+'\n')
end = time.time()
print('time',end-start)
print('output prefix', out[:100])
